title: Maryland high school shooter dead after exchange with officer: sheriff
text:
Maryland high school shooter dead after exchange with officer: sheriff 2:40am IST - 02:08 
A 17-year-old student shot and critically wounded two fellow students at a Maryland high school on Tuesday morning before being shot himself by a campus security officer. The student died about four hours after the incident. Rough Cut (no reporter narration).
